ns0:trans-unit.ns0:source: This section enables you to change the default pattern of your links. In order to use this functionality, PrestaShop's "Friendly URL" option must be enabled, and Apache's URL rewriting module (mod_rewrite) must be activated on your web server.

ns0:trans-unit.ns0:source: To add a keyword in your URL, use the {keyword} syntax. If the keyword is not empty, you can add text before or after the keyword with syntax {prepend:keyword:append}. For example {-hey-:meta_title} will add "-hey-my-title" in the URL if the meta title is set.
ns0:trans-unit.ns0:target: URL-dagi kalit so'zni qo'shish uchun {kalit so'z} sintaksisidan foydalaning.
